title: Tai Lopez - The infamous "Here in my Garage Ad" (Michael Sartain Podcast Clip)
description:
Tai Lopez (IG: @TaiLopez) is an investor, partner, and advisor to over 20 multi-million dollar businesses. Tai has created some of the most successful advertisements in the history of YouTube. He's currently the owner of RadioShack, Pier 1, Ralph & Russo and Stein Mart. Tai has a book club and hosts a podcast called The Tai Lopez Show. He has interviewed, Kobe Bryant, Hilary Clinton, Rihanna, Jordan Belfort,  Steven Spielberg, Mark Cuban, Chris Paul, Caron Butler & more. Tai also owns the largest book shipping club in the world, Mentor Box. He's currently launching the Original Garage NFT.
